{% endfor %}

## Requirements

1. Write the SKILL.md in English with proper Markdown formatting
2. Include YAML frontmatter with:
   - name: skill identifier (use kebab-case)
   - description: brief description of what this skill does
   - allowed-tools: list of allowed Claude Code tools for this skill

3. Structure the content as:
   - Brief introduction explaining the skill's purpose
   - Command section with all available commands
   - Best practices for using this skill
   - Common pitfalls to avoid

4. Make the content project-specific and actionable
5. Do NOT use placeholder text like "add your commands here" - use the actual commands provided

Output ONLY the complete SKILL.md content, no explanations or preamble.
